Package: kwb.resilience
Version: 0.1.0
Title: R Package for the Quantification of Technical Resilience
Description: kwb.resilience allows quantification of a number of 
    resilience indicators. Calculation requires a time series of
    performance values of a technical system, as well as values 
    for acceptable and worst case performance.
